data.description: Built in 2019, this charming two-story home enjoys a prime location adjacent to a peaceful reserve, ensuring privacy with no rear neighbors. The open floor plan allows flexibility, with the formal dining room easily adaptable as a home office. The kitchen features ample cabinets, elegant granite countertops, a breakfast bar, and a separate breakfast area flowing seamlessly into the family room. Large windows in the family room offer scenic views of the private backyard.    Notably, this property is in a non-flood zone and has never experienced flooding, providing peace of mind. Conveniently located near major transportation hubs, including George Bush Intercontinental Airport, Interstate 45, Hardy Toll Road, Beltway 8, and more. Don't miss out – schedule a viewing today!
